How to install git?
	WINOWS & MAC - https://git-scm.com/
			-- GIT BASH (Basic linux command in Windows)
	LINUX
		RHEL  - sudo yum install git
		UB  - sudo apt-get install git

=======================================
Git basic work flow
=========================================
step 1 - create a repo
$ git init

step 2 - create a file/code

step 3 - add a file to git [ WOrkING DIR TO STAGING AREA]
$ git add filename
ONE TIME
----------------
git config user.name "Rajesh Kumar"
git config user.email "devops@rajeshkumar.xyz"
git config --list
----------------
step 4 - commit a file to git [ STAGING AREA TO REPO ]
$ git commit -m"message why you are committing"

step 5 - see the history of commit
$ git log

Step 6 - what is the content of commit
$ git show commit-id

